event.description: Born in Newton/Massachusetts, raised in New England and now residing in Charleston, SC. Raised by his mother and sister, father was known writer and author Robert Michael who he saw sporadically. Americana artist Avi Jacob expresses the old soul of east coast America, twisting melodies from its' pitfalls and triumphs. Avi released his first single "Pick Up Truck" on February 26th, 2016. "Pickup Truck" lulls you to hypnotism, like a late night walk through forest, but expressed with the urgency of now. Avis lyrics tell the tale effortlessly leading us down the road less traveled. She has a very sexy vocal style that glides over breathy acoustic rock songs, as easily as it roars over classic rock inspired blues and R & B. Music on the Mall Summer Concert Series 6:00 PM Town Mall , Brunswick

Music on the Mall, Downtown Brunswickâs Summer Concert Series, presents FREE concerts Wednesday evenings at 6 PM throughout the summer on the Brunswick Town Mall (Green). Grab a blanket or chair, bring your family and friends, order a picnic dinner or dine at a local Brunswick restaurant, then relax and enjoy great music.

FREE Admission. All concerts start at 6 PM unless otherwise noted. In the case of inclement weather, rain date performances will be held on Thursdays when available.
